This module implements a BLE-based time synchronization mechanism inspired by
concepts from academic literature, including the "BlueSync" protocol.

No third-party code is included in this repository.

Contributions are welcome. By submitting a pull request, you agree that your
contribution will be licensed under the Apache 2.0 License.

Project Repository:
https://github.com/Tobi15/zephyr-bluesync-ble
